model.name: Keating2019 - Minimal model demonstrating SBML Level 3 packages.

body.p: Minimal model demonstrating SBML Level 3 packages. Model contains `layout`, `fbc` and `comp` information. Kinetic and constrained based models are supported. Keating et al. 2019 SBML Level 3: an extensible format for the exchange and reuse 1 of biological models (Manuscript under review)
